title: DDFP 393: Week 5 picks & Mascot Matchups
itunes:title: DDFP 393: Week 5 picks & Mascot Matchups
description:
Shek is joined by Elliot Harrison and Bucky Brooks to make their Week 5 picks during the “Red Challenge Flag Picks” segment. Plus, Shek introduces the “Mascot Matchups” segment, in which a steel worker and American Revolution patriot engage in a duel.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
